Class FcsSupport

java.lang.Object

  +--matrix.db.FcsSupport
public class FcsSupport
extends java.lang.Object

This class contains the functions need by other ADK classes to support the Fcs activities. These funtions are broken out into a separate src file to enable jdk 1.1 co-exsistence
